17-07-20T18:20:30.000Z","msg":"慘啊 都仲係冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今集講管理局條友想消除咲良田既能力<br />\n相麻唔會阻止呢件事, 而未來又睇到能力消除哂<br />\n但相麻又指示淺井做埋D奇怪野<br />\n到底佢係唔係指示淺井阻止呢件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n管理局條友之前出場既能力明明係修復D野<br />\n但係今集又話佢可以消除記憶?<br />\n另外係咖啡店到D人定哂又係咩意思<br />\n可能鎖定野條友鎖定哂間鋪頭D人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da9aad8913cf95c5ac525633de30e4b6bf72e3f7","tid":288030,"uid":13151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T13:58:26.000Z","msg":"覺得相麻最後會犧牲自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9a2cafa1c63807027461d472093c1e38acf3e04","tid":288030,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T09:57:02.000Z","msg":"等等<br />\n如果有劇本，點解要困住魔女"},{"pid":"636582c6fbc15b5c37019fa7683e7c433455baaf","tid":288030,"uid":75737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T10:29:03.000Z","msg":"第17集 <br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">惠由吸血鬼到知道左相麻係為左自己而死 但係我唔明咩意思 點樣為左佢?</span>"},{"pid":"69041a339977c38b408bbee1aa205f38b3d29940","tid":288030,"uid":49995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T10:31:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等等<br />\n如果有劇本，點解要困住魔女</blockquote><br />\n劇本係過去/已知發生既事實?<br />\n而寫既內容連能力者自己都冇得選擇<br />\n魔女就能夠預知未來<br />\n兩樣野黎好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4af5149db117177a216442a748d95d31d222dea6","tid":288030,"uid":53654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T03:07:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第17集 <br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">惠由吸血鬼到知道左相麻係為左自己而死 但係我唔明咩意思 點樣為左佢?</span></blockquote><br />\n可能之後講"},{"pid":"7c68a4fbaf88cfc7fbdabcd6d06244317c9cc15f","tid":288030,"uid":34896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T03:34:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>等等<br />\n如果有劇本，點解要困住魔女</blockquote><br 